==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Solanaceous
<hw>Sol`a*na"ceous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>Of or pertaining to plants of the natural order
<ord>Solanaceae</ord>, of which the nightshade (<gen>Solanum</gen>) is
the type. The order includes also the tobacco, ground cherry, tomato,
eggplant, red pepper, and many more.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Soland</ent>⟦br⟧
